Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:26.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:31.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:31.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:37.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:37.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:45.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:45.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:47.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:47.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:53.27,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:53.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:58.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:00:58.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:01:04.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:04.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:09.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:09.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:11.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:15.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:15.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:20.47,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:20.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:26.03,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:26.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:31.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:31.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:36.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:36.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:42.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:42.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:47.37,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:47.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:55.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:55.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.79,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:57.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:01.09,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:01.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:06.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:06.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:11.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:11.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:17.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:17.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:25.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:03:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, depressed after losing his brother \NAce in the war against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,realized the importance of friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sent a message to his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Living through Hell! \NSanji's Fight for His Manhood!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the small Sky Island - Weatheria...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There she is!\N--We found her finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How could you fool us?\N--You didn't just steal our research notes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But you toyed with...\N--Our pure hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender yourself now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thieving girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The research notes!\N--The Weather ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the hostage - Mr. Haredas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unforgivable even if you return them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I regret what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, we can't trust her!\N--Let's strip her and banish her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so... naughty...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Naughty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naughty...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no! I didn't mean it \Nthat way! What I wanted to say is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She changed the subject... \NShe changed the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tut!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just tut?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! How terrible! That's an unjust charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, is it my fault?! Didn't \Nyou guys hear that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I don't think so...\N--Don't get fooled by her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a mistake! I \Nwouldn't do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maybe I misheard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's manipulating them completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--She's wicked!\N--Let's kick her out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm sorry! I regret what I've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could we trust you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I understand. Alright, \Nto show you how sorry I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna jump into the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me in the afterworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We made her cry!\N--Don't jump the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too young to put an end to your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm gonna stay here a little \Nlonger and study about weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my name is Nami. You \Ncan call me Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need a house to live in. \NEverybody needs a little privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a nice and comfortable bed, a \Njet tub, and a big closet as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, grandpas in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do it! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Haredas, come in! Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were desperate to get \Noff of this island before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What made you change your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot going on. \NCould you tell me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weatheria travels on the wind and \Nwanders around the world in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes we descend to get \Nsome supplies and information
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then continue on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Information?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to check records.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still a lot of unknown \Nweather conditions and phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that are difficult to fathom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's this?!\N--Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:06:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning strikes like rain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, literally "like rain."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it strikes that island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That island is in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're willing to go to that sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to open your mind to the unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a big world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you. Teach me, Haredas-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything that you know about...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the weather of the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I am! All of my \Nfriends' lives are in my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a navigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take \Nresponsibility when we're on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to navigate the way \Nwherever my captain wants to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy wants to become \Nthe King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:08:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to improve myself as a navigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your captain must be happy to have \Nsuch a thoughtful crew member.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I have no choice.\N--You have no choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He's so boastful, but he \Ndoesn't know anything about the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always does ridiculous \Nthings. If I left him alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I left him alone, he'd \Nprobably end up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:09:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not-so-bright and high-maintenance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be hard to have a captain like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. That's why I wanna help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like he helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, tell me about the Weather ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that simple. That's one of \Nthe great inventions of Weatheria!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you misuse it, it could \Nturn the world upside down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be used as a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, that's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't smile like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, on the Mechanical \NIsland Future Land Baldimore...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The unexpected bombing at \NDr. Vegapunk's laboratory!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't found who did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too much to say that it \Nwas a greatest loss of our time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any information?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there was an intruder \Nthat looks like a gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How mysterious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to reach the harbor of this \Nisland, you need a large ice-breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one has seen one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:11:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that the intruder was Cyborg \NFranky of the Straw Hat Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's just been seen on Sabaody \NArchipelago within the past month and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we don't know how he \Ncould've gotten to Baldimore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Gorilla! The search team \Nis leaving for the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'm coming with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hidden entrance has been \Nuncovered by the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise. We didn't \Nknow about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was another laboratory!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The working cyborg animals \Nmust have been created here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't break anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't talk to me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the laboratory that was blown away,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there \Nwere some far-out inventions useful in daily life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what I wanted to know about \Nare the weapon inventions,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:12:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like the ones here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great! Everything from \Nbattleships to human cells...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did he come up with \Nall these kinds of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna live here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Live here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come down the mountain sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to get more cola from your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't tell anybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't cause you trouble \Nbecause I'll live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic every time you see my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't look at us!\N--That scary face is getting scarier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this? A tiger rug!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's not bad...\N--F-F-F-Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's cold especially my legs.\N--Why don't you wear your pants?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay, now it's warm!\N--Why don't you just wear your pants?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you said you wanted to get off \Nof this island. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not much but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to sail on the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I built!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You let me hold a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a great ship! I'll take good care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want these shorts back,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll have to join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought me out into this big world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll cross many seas and have \Ntons of battles and challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when we get to the end of the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will call it "the ship of dreams."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Thousand Sunny still \Nhas some life in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only captain who can make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..."the ship of dreams."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll acquire skills that'll enable us to have
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an even more harrowing adventure than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Luffy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the tiger is burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster?! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Luffy, we have to get over \Nthe rough sea of the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This incident will be known \Naround the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the Legend of Baldimore's \NSacred Burning Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the Kamabakka Kingdom, Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what was it you saw in the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got so calm all of the sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I received Luffy's message because it's \Nexclusively for his friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't believe that I'm his \Nfriend, I'm not gonna tell you, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:16:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who made this meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.91,0:16:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you have quite a discriminating palate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes good and oddly, I feel \Nlike I'm overflowing with energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! It's a dish of aggression!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of chefs who \Ncan make that on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes!\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes!\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the beautiful tough \Nbodies of these candies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And their gentle hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candies grew like this by \Neating the dish of aggression!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you eat is important for your condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,physique, and personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It builds the whole human body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all the people in the \Nworld drink milk everyday...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there'll be less crime - don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:17:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's good to be aggressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food builds body? I never \Nthought about it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can help them building their \Nbodies with daily meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But besides that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what'll I do if Nami-san and Robin-chan \Nget sexier than they are now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What should we do with this guy?\N--What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm burning with passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me how to cook the dish of aggression!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is "No!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was very wishful thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This "99 - Vital Recipe" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a part of the New Kama Kempo \Ntechniques - Training for Married Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just teach it to a nobody like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna learn it, you gotta \Nhave a girlish heart and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...learn the New Kama Kempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't born to become friends with ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...love ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heehaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite a reasonable man. I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll give you a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hand out the recipes to 99 grand masters
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the New Kama Kempo on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a real pirate, get \Nall the recipes from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, every new kamas on this island
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will try to put this sweet \Ndress on you day and night!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you can maintain your manhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:19:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji-kun!\N--We won't let you sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sweet dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring back the exciting \Nfeelings of wearing skirts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! It's nice to be girly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...vs. the home of the New Kama Kempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can win this fight, I'll give \Nyou a ship, too! You can have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join my group!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be the cook on my pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see idiots like that \Nevery once in a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:20:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ones who will fight to the death once \Nthey've set their eyes on a target...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear your answer - \Ndoes that mean you give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if you lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I win...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I beat all of them, I bet I'll \Nbe much stronger than I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if hundreds of weapons are built in,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he can be defeated by someone with \Na spear of blind determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy, don't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm hoping to go some \Nday... to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the right time yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Say... do you know the All Blue? \N--No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't?! It's a miracle sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We both have foolish dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to achieve my goal, the All Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.88,0:21:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll come along... on your journey \Nto become "King of the Pirates"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the cook for your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, if I can see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you the greatest \Nsupport in the world as a cook
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.74,0:21:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I live through...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! We won't go easy on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.41,0:22:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me the cold shoulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shut up!\N--Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.52,0:22:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.80,0:22:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose either, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.93,0:22:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the recipe from me - Caroline!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get revenge for the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.38,0:23:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's messages have \Nreached his friends safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.17,0:23:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking Luffy's feelings to their own hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his friends make a decision \Ntoward pursuing a new goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They meet at the captain's side once more,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.28,0:23:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their sights set on the day they'll \Nset out on a new adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Will Get Much, Much Stronger! \NZoro's Pledge to His Captain!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.87,0:23:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
